"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426643","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2015-11-10","The Government is actively considering the findings of the review into survivor benefits in occupational pension schemes. The Review provided important information on the benefits, costs and other effects of eliminating or reducing differences in survivor benefit provision. It is important that the findings of the Review are considered thoroughly so that we arrive at the right conclusion. We will respond to the Review in due course.","North Swindon","Justin Tomlinson",,"2015-11-10T14:20:02.697Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426643/answer","Biography information for Justin Tomlinson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426643/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426643/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2015-11-05","Survivor Benefits in Occupational Pension Schemes Review","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, when he will respond to the Review of Survivor Benefits in Occupational Pension Schemes, published in June 2014.","false","Biography information for Diana Johnson","Kingston upon Hull North","Diana Johnson","15070"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426644","Department for Work and Pensions","false","2015-11-12","<p>The first phase of the ‘Trusted Partner’ pilot started on Monday 28<sup>th</sup> September with 6 landlords all of whom are located within the Pathfinder areas.</p>","North Swindon","Justin Tomlinson",,"2015-11-12T10:55:02.36Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426644/answer","Biography information for Justin Tomlinson","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426644/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426644/answer",,,,,"29","Work and Pensions","Work and Pensions","2015-11-05","Universal Credit: Housing","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Work and Pensions, how many social housing providers in the four pathfinder areas for universal credit have applied for trusted partner status to allow for direct payment of the housing costs element in certain circumstances.","false","Biography information for Emily Thornberry","Islington South and Finsbury","Emily Thornberry","15086"
