"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426243","Department for Transport","false","2015-11-10","<p><strong></strong>We have committed to setting out the Government’s plan for the HS2 Phase Two route in an update to the House before the end of this year.</p>","Scarborough and Whitby","Mr Robert Goodwill",,"2015-11-10T15:06:05.207Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426243/answer","Biography information for Mr Robert Goodwill","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426243/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426243/answer",,,,,"27","Transport","Transport","2015-11-04","High Speed 2 Railway Line","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Transport, when he plans to announce the finalised route phase two of the High Speed 2 rail line; and if he will make a statement.","false","Biography information for Fiona Bruce","Congleton","Fiona Bruce","14735"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426244","Ministry of Defence","false","2015-11-10","<p>Where external recruitment to Senior Civil Service (SCS) posts is required, recruitment agencies and head-hunters may be engaged to assist with campaigns. The costs of agency services include search, advertisement, response handling, assessment and support to selection panels.</p><br /><p>Details of spend on SCS recruitment with external agencies and head-hunters, by calendar year, are as follows:</p><br /><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Calendar Year</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Spend</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2010</p></td><td><p>£121,000</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2011</p></td><td><p>£144,000</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2012</p></td><td><p>£284,000</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2013</p></td><td><p>£373,000</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2014</p></td><td><p>£583,000</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>2015 (to 31 March)</p></td><td><p>£33,000</p></td></tr></tbody></table><br /><p>Note: information held by the Ministry of Defence extends to 31 March 2015 only; from 1 April 2015 recruitment for SCS posts has been managed centrally by Civil Service Resourcing.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2015-11-10T16:28:00.833Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426244/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426244/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426244/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2015-11-04","Ministry of Defence: Senior Civil Servants","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, what estimate he has made of the cost of using external agencies for recruitment to senior Civil Service posts in his Department in each of the last five years for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","14894"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426245","HM Treasury","false","2015-11-11","<p>HM Treasury have not had a separate budget for senior civil service recruitment in the last 5 years and has no record of using external agencies to recruit to senior civil service posts during this period.</p>","West Worcestershire","Harriett Baldwin",,"2015-11-11T11:39:23.077Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426245/answer","Biography information for Harriett Baldwin","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426245/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426245/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2015-11-04","Treasury: Senior Civil Servants","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, what estimate he has made of the cost of using external agencies for recruitment to senior Civil Service posts in his Department in each of the last five years for which figures are available.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","14893"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426246","Cabinet Office","false","2015-11-10","<p>The Government publishes statistics on the operation of the Freedom of Information Act 2000 within central government, including on timeliness. These reports can be accessed at the following webpage: <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/government-foi-statistics" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/government-foi-statistics</a>.</p>","West Suffolk","Matthew Hancock",,"2015-11-10T10:59:30.527Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426246/answer","Biography information for Matt Hancock","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426246/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/426246/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2015-11-04","Cabinet Office: Freedom of Information","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what average time his Department took to respond to freedom of information requests in each year since 2005.","false","Biography information for Louise Haigh","Sheffield, Heeley","Louise Haigh","14898"
